        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 11. Details of two arachnid inclusions, to same scale. A. Partially preserved oribatid mite (AMNH LC-D1), ventral view, showing long legs with swollen podites and large claws, similar to those in Damaeoidea. B. Partial pseudoscorpion, ventral view (AMNH GC-A8b)." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4598595/files/figure.png" .

